OL,3,CMuslims across Wales gather to
OL,4,Ccelebrate Eid
OL,6,FMuslims across Wales are celebrating
OL,7,FEid as Ramadan comes to an end.
OL,9,FEid al-Fitr, meaning festival of the
OL,10,Fbreaking of the fast, is celebrated at
OL,11,Fthe end of Ramadan - when many Muslims
OL,12,Ffast.
OL,14,FRamadan is the ninth month of the
OL,15,FIslamic calendar. It is during this
OL,16,Fmonth that Muslims believe the first
OL,17,Fverses of the Quran were revealed to
OL,18,Fthe Prophet Muhammad.
