OL,3,CMuslims across Wales gather to
OL,4,Ccelebrate Eid
OL,6,FDuring this month, Muslims are
OL,7,Frequired to fast, give to charity,
OL,8,Fshow kindness and patience and to
OL,9,Fstrengthen their relationship with God.
OL,11,FCelebrations are taking place across
OL,12,FWales, including in Cardiff where
OL,13,Fprayers, singing, games, and other
OL,14,Factivities have been happening in
OL,15,FSophia Gardens.
