OL,3,CMuslims across Wales gather to
OL,4,Ccelebrate Eid
OL,6,FSameer Alyas was among the team that
OL,7,Forganised the event with Sophia
OL,8,FGardens Cricket Ground, where the
OL,9,Fevent was held. Speaking to ITV Wales,
OL,10,Fhe said: "We expected 300-350 but we
OL,11,Fgot at least 600-700 turning out
OL,12,Ftoday, so it's been a successful
OL,13,Fevent."
OL,15,F"It's a big event for us and this is
OL,16,Four first official prayer we've done
OL,17,Fin such a big venue, on such a big
OL,18,Fscale. Hopefully, in the future it
OL,19,Fwill help us build relations with
OL,20,FGlamorgan Cricket and the local
OL,21,Fcommunity."
