OL,3,CMuslims across Wales gather to
OL,4,Ccelebrate Eid
OL,6,FPeople of all ages gathered at the
OL,7,Fcricket ground to take part in prayers
OL,8,Fand activities.
OL,10,F"It's a day to celebrate with family,
OL,11,Fto receive gifts and just share the
OL,12,Fday with loved ones," said Joudy Al-
OL,13,FMouselli who attended the event. "It's
OL,14,Freally exciting (to be here). The UK
OL,15,Fis doing a good job with Eid prayers."
OL,17,FSpeaking to ITV Wales, one man
OL,18,Fcelebrating with his family said: "I'm
OL,19,Fsuper excited, I'm over the moon - my
OL,20,Fkids around me, my wife with me.
