OL,3,CMuslims across Wales gather to
OL,4,Ccelebrate Eid
OL,6,F"I've been waiting for it for nearly a
OL,7,Fyear. That year, I felt a bit lonely
OL,8,Fbecause I don't have family around me,
OL,9,Fbut today when we came here to
OL,10,Fcelebrate Eid with other Muslim
OL,11,Fbrothers and sisters, I felt I had a
OL,12,Fhuge community with me, so I'm over
OL,13,Fthe moon."
